WEBVTT

00:03:59.520 --> 00:04:04.319
We have reached 60,000 women
with this breast check up

00:04:04.320 --> 00:04:06.999
and have detected 50 breast cancer cases.

00:04:07.000 --> 00:04:08.580
And I am happy to share

00:04:08.580 --> 00:04:11.735
that with the help of the governments
of Maharashtra and Rajasthan,

00:04:11.735 --> 00:04:15.290
we will be able to take this invention
to hundreds of thousands of women.

00:04:15.290 --> 00:04:18.720
(Applause)

00:04:18.720 --> 00:04:21.358
Just a few months before my wedding,

00:04:21.360 --> 00:04:23.719
my mother-in-law was detected
with breast cancer,

00:04:23.720 --> 00:04:27.279
and she has in the true sense
been my inspiration for this journey.

00:04:27.280 --> 00:04:28.679
She is well today,

00:04:28.680 --> 00:04:33.839
but I know eight such women 
who were detected with breast cancer,